{"tid":1188503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天官校長在學校門口沒收「反送中」單張，唔俾拎入學校","createTime":"2019-06-06T09:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T02:15:13.000Z","uid":20058,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f541d04d0920c7c84148153c69ca2485c906f473","tid":1188503,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:50:53.000Z","msg":"【校友自發 學校失去蔡元培校長的氣魄】<br />\n<br />\n昨天早上，有幾位天水圍官立中學的校友在學校外圍派「反送中」單張給同學、老師及家長。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，好多同學家長也有接，想了解《逃犯條例》的謬論。不過，我們其後知道：「校長系學校門口收曬你地啲單張，吾俾拎入學校&quot;😑」。<br />\n<br />\n歷史讓我們認識很多開明的校長，包括蔡元培先生。可惜，我們香港的校長應不是，或校長們已沒有熟讀中西歷史吧！<br />\n<br />\n#明天星期四<br />\n#同學仍可自發<br />\n#需要單張可PM我們<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/789610291181847/posts/1414875958655274?s=100001313257075&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F789610291181847%2Fposts%2F1414875958655274%3Fs%3D100001313257075%26sfns%3Dmo&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BgmWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=96fc0b19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/789610291181847/posts/1414875958655274?s=100001313257075&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"8461edc67e7f8a9f942352a168ce93ca755bd0b3","tid":1188503,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:53:38.000Z","msg":"我成日都唔明, 點解唔放學時派？"},{"pid":"72be0693d72995472d55b7b522a82af1736ed0f6","tid":1188503,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:55:02.000Z","msg":"你肯定你早得過中學生放學放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d721a71c1ec5f2286ddad387af9d48c026dbf8d","tid":1188503,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8461edc67e7f8a9f942352a168ce93ca755bd0b3","tid":1188503,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:53:38.000Z","msg":"我成日都唔明, 點解唔放學時派？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:58:55.000Z","msg":"放學時間散多<br />\n人流都冇明顯咁集中"},{"pid":"72238b5cbf1a12e616786bad5881d6bbb493f62d","ti